支付状态后暂不支付，之后在微信客户端对兑换券进行退款操作，然后再将之前客户端的订单取消，这时候客户端上竟可以重新获取兑换券，此种方式分文未付骗取了一份兑换券。 第二个是先在APP客户端用套餐兑换券下单待支付，在微信客户端退掉兑换券，再在APP客户端用兑换券支付，这时便可以支付成功并获得取餐码，此种方式等于分文未付骗取了一份套餐。 发现这个漏洞后，徐某“喜出望外”。从当年4月起，除了自己这样点餐操作，徐某还做起了“副业”：将诈骗得来的套餐产品通过线上交易软件低价出售给他人，从中获利。 同时，他还与同学有“福”同享，将犯罪方法当面或通过网络传授给丁某等4名同学。截至同年10月案发，徐某的行为造成百盛公司损失5.8万余元，丁某等四人造成百盛公司损失0.89万元至4.7万元不等。"},"attached_info":"CkAI8vXY+Kmfh8crEAMaCDY0MjQ5ODI3IJHc6IQGMJEBONskQBJyCTQ1ODg2MjU0NHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"194 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-21c1a1c56c3678f0c3c0f019affd4919_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"19_1620806874.1494827","card_id":"Q_453500291","target":{"id":453500291,"title":"为什么手机计算器上50%+50%=0.75?","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/453500291","type":"question","created":1617848598,"answer_count":335,"follower_count":1917,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[488,1291,12990,51795,139584],"comment_count":31,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj8I8vXY+Kmfh8crEAMaCDYzMDU3MzYxIJbSuYMGMB84/Q5AE3IJNDUzNTAwMjkxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"182 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/80/v2-559ed0a10a9b0f784e6119035954ceb3_720w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"20_1620806874.149945","card_id":"Q_457336083","target":{"id":457336083,"title":"如何评价漫画家谏山创最近的访谈内容？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/457336083","type":"question","created":1619793002,"answer_count":85,"follower_count":288,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[83624,211865,219515,665529,686987],"comment_count":10,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"根据访谈内容，他是右翼吗（图源自贴吧的咪西大佬） （